        "inventory": [
          {
            "itemId": "c3d5e4f6-7a8b-4c9d-8e1f-2a3b4c5d6e7f",
            "quantity": "1",
            "dropChance": 0.75
          },
          {
            "itemId": "d4e6f5a7-8b9c-4d0e-9f2a-3b4c5d6e7f8a",
            "quantity": "1",
            "dropChance": 0.5
          },
          {
            "itemId": "e5f7a6b8-9c0d-4e1f-aa3b-4c5d6e7f8a9b",
            "quantity": "1",
            "dropChance": 0.2
          }
        ],
        "images": [],
        "notes": "<p><strong>Combat Notes:</strong> The troll will attack the nearest creature and press the assault relentlessly. It uses <span class=\"wiki-link wiki-link--found\" data-wiki-id=\"b8c0d9e1-2f3a-4b4c-ad6e-7f8a9b0c1d2e\" data-wiki-type=\"abilities\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\">Thick Hide</span> as a reaction when struck, and leads every round with <span class=\"wiki-link wiki-link--found\" data-wiki-id=\"a7b9c8d0-1e2f-4a3b-9c5d-6e7f8a9b0c1d\" data-wiki-type=\"abilities\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\">Crushing Slam</span>. It will not flee.</p><p><strong><span class=\"wiki-link wiki-link--found\" data-wiki-id=\"f6a8b7c9-0d1e-4f2a-8b4c-5d6e7f8a9b0c\" data-wiki-type=\"abilities\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\">Regeneration</span>:</strong> Remind players after the first round that wounds are closing — the clock is ticking. Without fire or acid damage, attrition heavily favors the troll.</p>",
        "createdAt": "2024-09-01T13:00:00.000Z",
